#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.arange.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.arange"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:1 of
msgid "Return evenly spaced values within a given interval."
msgstr "返回给定区间内均匀间隔的值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:3 of
msgid ""
"Values are generated within the half-open interval ``[start, stop)`` (in "
"other words, the interval including `start` but excluding `stop`). For "
"integer arguments the function is equivalent to the Python built-in "
"`range <http://docs.python.org/lib/built-in-funcs.html>`_ function, but "
"returns a tensor rather than a list."
msgstr ""
"值在半开区间 ``[start, stop)`` 内生成（换句话说，区间包括 `start` 但不"
"包括 `stop`）。对于整数参数，此函数等价于 Python 内置的 `range <http://"
"docs.python.org/lib/built-in-funcs.html>`_ 函数，但返回的是张量而不是列表"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:9 of
msgid ""
"When using a non-integer step, such as 0.1, the results will often not be"
" consistent.  It is better to use ``linspace`` for these cases."
msgstr ""
"当使用非整数步长（如 0.1）时，结果通常不一致。在这种情况下，最好使用 ``"
"linspace``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:12 of
msgid ""
"Start of interval.  The interval includes this value.  The default start "
"value is 0."
msgstr "区间的起始值。区间包括该值。默认起始值为 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:15 of
msgid ""
"End of interval.  The interval does not include this value, except in "
"some cases where `step` is not an integer and floating point round-off "
"affects the length of `out`."
msgstr ""
"区间的结束值。区间不包括该值，除非在某些 `step` 不是整数且浮点数舍入影响 "
"`out` 长度的情况下。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:19 of
msgid ""
"Spacing between values.  For any output `out`, this is the distance "
"between two adjacent values, ``out[i+1] - out[i]``.  The default step "
"size is 1.  If `step` is specified as a position argument, `start` must "
"also be given."
msgstr ""
"值之间的间隔。对于任何输出 `out`，这是两个相邻值之间的距离，``out[i+1] - "
"out[i]``。默认步长为 1。如果 `step` 作为位置参数指定，则必须同时给出 `"
"start`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:24 of
msgid ""
"The type of the output tensor.  If `dtype` is not given, infer the data "
"type from the other input arguments."
msgstr "输出张量的类型。如果未给出 `dtype`，则从其他输入参数推断数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:27 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:30 of
msgid ""
"**arange** -- Tensor of evenly spaced values.  For floating point "
"arguments, the length of the result is ``ceil((stop - start)/step)``.  "
"Because of floating point overflow, this rule may result in the last "
"element of `out` being greater than `stop`."
msgstr ""
"**arange** -- 均匀间隔值的张量。对于浮点参数，结果的长度为 ``ceil((stop -"
" start)/step)``。由于浮点溢出，此规则可能导致 `out` 的最后一个元素大于 `"
"stop`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:30 of
msgid "**arange** -- Tensor of evenly spaced values."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:32 of
msgid ""
"For floating point arguments, the length of the result is ``ceil((stop - "
"start)/step)``.  Because of floating point overflow, this rule may result"
" in the last element of `out` being greater than `stop`."
msgstr ""
"对于浮点数参数，结果的长度为 ``ceil((stop - start)/step)``。由于浮点数"
"溢出，此规则可能导致 `out` 的最后一个元素大于 `stop`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:40 of
msgid ":py:obj:`linspace`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:41 of
msgid "Evenly spaced numbers with careful handling of endpoints."
msgstr "均匀间隔的数字，并仔细处理端点。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:43 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ogrid`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:44 of
msgid "Tensors of evenly spaced numbers in N-dimensions."
msgstr "N 维空间中均匀间隔数字的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:46 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mgrid`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.arange.arange:47 of
msgid "Grid-shaped tensors of evenly spaced numbers in N-dimensions."
msgstr "N 维空间中均匀间隔数字的网格形状张量。"

